command to create topic 

got to any of kafka folder ,

stay outside bin folder, dont enter becz, will use /bin to creat topic

use below command
=>
./bin/kafka-topics.sh --create --topic Email-PN-Queue --partitions 3 --replication-factor 3 --bootstrap-server localhost:9092, localhost:9093, localhost:9094


